{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JZ7cmNZZkp82ndK5epjGGA","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's what was implemented:\n\n**Files created:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/__tests__/run-pipeline.test.ts` — 21 integration tests covering all 4 cli-verifiable ACs\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/tests/fixtures/sample-stream.ndjson` — realistic NDJSON fixture with 21 lines covering all event types (tool_use, text_delta, thinking_delta, hook_started, hook_response, init, message_start/stop/delta, result)\n\n**Files modified:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/6-2-verify-stream-json-pipeline-e2e.md` — status changed to `review`, ACs 1-4 checked off\n\n**Test coverage by AC:**\n- **AC1** (2 tests): Pipes full NDJSON fixture through `makeLineHandler -> parseStreamLine` chain; tests chunk-boundary resilience by splitting fixture into varying-size buffers\n- **AC2** (5 tests): Asserts tool-start/tool-input/tool-complete/text arrive in correct order with correct payloads (tool names, IDs, partial JSON, text content, cost/sessionId)\n- **AC3** (6 tests): Verifies thinking_delta, hook_started, hook_response, init, message_start/stop/delta all return null (silently ignored, no errors)\n- **AC4** (7 tests): Verifies [SUCCESS], [WARN] (retry exceeded), [WARN] (retry N/M), [LOOP] iteration, ANSI-stripped messages, non-ralph lines, and mixed NDJSON+ralph on stderr\n- **AC5**: Left unchecked — requires manual verification (integration-required)\n\n**Test file placement:** Story specified `tests/run-pipeline.test.ts` but vitest config has `root: 'src'`. Placed at `src/__tests__/run-pipeline.test.ts` so vitest discovers it. The fixture file is at `tests/fixtures/sample-stream.ndjson` as specified.\n\nAll 2912 tests pass (113 test files) including the new 21 tests.\n\n## Session Issues\n\n- **Test file location diverges from story spec**: Stor