{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01DtWxeXgiFhm1ZUk1hdTk78","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MmPmN4MSGEYqgPSAbUdZLf","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **All 4 automatable ACs passed** with 48 total assertions.","new_string":"- **All 4 automatable ACs passed** with 48 total assertions.\n\n### epic-6-retrospective (2026-03-21T11:37Z)\n\n- **Epic numbering collision:** Two sprints reused \"Epic 6\" for different epics. Stale retro file persisted across 4+ session retros before being overwritten.\n- **Action item carry-forward rate ~100%:** Retro action items are generated but never executed. Process failure, not documentation gap.\n- **Story 6-1 harder than expected:** NFR9 300-line limit forced 3-file split not anticipated during story creation.\n- **Story 6-2 harder than expected:** `makeLineHandler` was untestable closure — required production refactor to extract `createLineProcessor`.\n- **Known tech debt:** Cost accumulation data loss for events before `sprintInfo` init."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":435,"cache_read_input_tokens":61134,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":435},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eb26302c-c52a-41c7-9204-5eb8c12a854c","uuid":"d4292a21-824f-4a83-a64f-206c8b837f21"}
